name: Ronnie Moore
bio:
Follower of Christ ✝️ 
🎤 TV Broadcaster
@Bass_Nation and @sportfishingchampionship 🎣
📺🎙: ESPN, FS1, CBS Sports 
Married to @Sarah.ks.moore ❤️

social_posts.post_text:
Went to our favorite Christmas Tree farm and cut down our tree 🎄

Marlow ate steak 🥩

Read Day 1 of Advent ✝️

Pretty solid December 1st for the Moore’s 🙌🏻 #blessed #thankful
So about last night. Time portal back to a 70’s Murder Mystery Studio Christmas party. My best attempt to mimic a generation I never physically saw. 😂🕺🏼🪩

Very busy, but fun and fulfilling weekend with my girls and church family. From a late night Sunday School party to Saturday’s Christmas Mall and finally the Sunday IBCLR Christmas performance. 

Our girly did so well. Grateful to share what Christmas means to us, with her. @sarah.ks.moore

Hogs win in Little Rock! 

Spent the game with my girls and my work family. Marlow was a big hit and did so great during the game. 🙌🏻

Christmas Eve. Such a time of anticipation and excitement for so many, but years ago, there was panic for two parents as they sought a place to have their baby. 

The Savior of the world was on his way and they had to trust, not fear and care for Emmanuel! What an honor that would be. Grateful for their faithfulness and Jesus’ perfect birth, life and legacy. 

“And she will have a son, and you are to name him Jesus, for he will save his people from their sins.” 
- Matthew 1:21 🙌🏻
Raise your hand if you had a fun first Christmas 🙋🏼‍♀️👨‍👩‍👧
First post of 2023 and we still love smiling and sleeping 5 more mins, please.

I never wanna forget these small moments! They loom large in a child’s life and impact them more than we know. If it’s been a good or bad day, the 5 mins of Bible time with Marlow is always so special.

Made a special trip down to Waco to watch the Hogs play Baylor with @zach_moore10. What a wildly fun game to witness and even though the Razorbacks came up short, I had a blast with @altonjrfishing and @altonjonesfishing. Thanks for the hospitality and the seats! #basketball #cbb #baylor #arkansas  #woopig #jesusisbetter

This week we hit 100 days in a row of reading the Bible! So many great things happened in 2022, but starting this routine with Sarah and Marlow was by far a top notch moment. I’ve learned so much during this time and I wish I would’ve started reading the Bible to her nightly earlier. Can’t wait until it’s 1,000 and 2,000.

Gah lee, I love you so much! Happy Birthday Say Say. I’ve learned to be a best friend, a husband, a man and a dad since we got together back in 2011. You’re incredible and I’m so grateful for your presence in my life. 

The 1st day of the 2nd month will always be special because it’s your day! Happy “29!” (Schmidt voice) Birthday. ❤️

Humbling and motivating moments this weekend. We had the opportunity to dedicate Marlow to the Lord today. 

She isn’t any closer to being a believer as she was last night, but this was a pledge from Sarah and I that we would raise her to love Jesus and that those who are near and dear to us would hold us accountable. 

Being a servant to the most high God is such a freeing feeling. It isn’t oppressive, it’s opportunity. Lord, let us live in your will.
The goal is to show you so much love daily, that Feb. 14th becomes just another day ❤️

Year 10 with B.A.S.S.

What a journey it’s been and what a journey it’ll continue to be! Tomorrow kicks off my 10th season working with @bass_nation. From BassTrakk, blogs, photos, the War Room, College TV, video and Bassmaster LIVE it’s all been so fulfilling. 

Day 1 of the 2023 Elite Series season kicks off tomorrow. Let’s do it! See you at 8 am ET on Bassmaster.com

For complete transparency, here are my @bass_nation Fantasy Fishing teams at Lake Okeechobee. Who did you pick in Rapala and who did you burn in Drain the Lake? #fantasyfishing #basselite #bassmaster #okeechobee

Congrats to @tyler_rivet_trfishing for winning the 2023 @bass_nation Elite at Lake Okeechobee with 86-15. He did it his way this week en route to his first Bassmaster victory. Who would’ve thought, livescope at Okeechobee to get the win on unpressured fish. #basselite #bassmaster #fishing #okeechobee

Knocked out the Bassmaster LIVE preview show for Lake Seminole this morning with Tommy and the gang. Really looking forward to this event. If I had to circle two lakes on the schedule for 2023, it would be Seminole and Murray. 

Join us at 8 am ET everyday (a little earlier for FB LIVE) and stay through the weekend for the shows on FS1. @bass_nation #bassmasterlive #basslive #seminole #basselite

Congrats to @joeycifuentesfishing on his @bass_nation Elite Series title! Cifuentes weighed 85-2 over four days, including a 26-1 bag on Day 2, to win at Lake Seminole. Cowboy got it done. #basselite #bassmaster #lakeseminole
Holy smokes, spending Monday with y’all was so fun.

9 future @bass_nation Elite Series pros are sitting in this room. 

Bassmaster Open at Lake Eufaula starts in the morning 💪🏻

The 1st day of the 2023 @bass_nation Opens season is in the books. They caught the heck out of em at Lake Eufaula. 25 pounds is on top, 20 pounds to get Top 12, 15 pounds has you in 65th. 

Unfortunately the wind is going to blow big time from the wrong direction tomorrow and the decision has already been made for the full field to wrap this puppy up on Saturday. Should be a shootout on a lake that is going off! #bassopens #bassmaster #fishing #lakeeufaula

Duddeeee

It felt good to be back. Even for a week. The first Bassmaster Open is in the books 👌🏻

It was great seeing old faces, new faces, excitement, motivation, drive, passion and so many other things this week. There was a different vibe in the air that comes around once in a while. Great things coming for the Opens and the EQ dynamic. #bassmaster #lakeeufaula #fishing #bassopens @bass_nation

DNOW 2023

The final year with our group. In 2018, I was bugged for weeks to be one of their leaders. I finally said yes and it was one of the best decisions I’ve ever made. 

This senior group has been through a pandemic and despite the obstacles, became even more consistent in attending and growing their faith. They were there when Sarah and I went through loss, they were there early and they stayed late. When I challenged them to 6 am Bible study, they said yes. 

My life is forever better because I know this group of kids. Let’s make the last few months absolutely incredible and let’s see how God can use us. @ibclrstudents
Are you ready? Whole squad ready! Classic TV interviews are done, final practice is in the morning. Day 1 is drawing near! @bass_nation #bassmasterclassic
Night of Champions! Spent an hour talking with the anglers and their significant others tonight! Check it out on Facebook and on YouTube! @bass_nation

You can’t win the Bassmaster Classic on Day 1, but you sure can lose it. These guys did their job and are in the hunt 1/3 of the way through the gauntlet. 

The race this week is a little bit of marathon, lotta bit of sprint. #bassmasterclassic @bass_nation
I’m unworthy to be in the presence of greatness this week, especially with what I said a while back about smallmouth 😂😬 @gussyoutdoors @bass_nation

Jeff Gustafson is the 2023 Bassmaster Classic Champion!

He becomes the first Canadian to win the Bassmaster Classic and only the 2nd International Angler to win the World Championship of bass fishing. 

@gussyoutdoors @bass_nation 
#bassmasterclassic #bassmaster #knoxville #tennesseeriver

Gussy “Knox” their socks off and takes the 53rd Bassmaster Classic trophy north of the border. 

He may not have the keys to the city but he definitely has full authority of the boat ramps up and down Ft. Loudoun and Tellico. #bassmasterclassic @bass_nation
“I’m here, let’s eat pancakes” - Marlow, probably
Are you kidding me?

An amazing day of reflection and praise to Jesus! 

He has overcome the Grave, he has overcome Sin. Forever. Oh death where is your victory, oh death where is your sting?

“Why are you looking among the dead for someone who is alive? He isn’t here! He is risen from the dead! Remember what he told you back in Galilee.” Luke 24:6

Fulfilling this prophecy solidified every truth ever spoken or written in the Bible. Praise God for his perfect plan and love for his children 🙌🏻

Sharing this with Marlow today and this week brought me to tears. I pray she loves and trusts in Jesus as her Savior one day 🙏🏻

Marlow’s first interaction with a bass was long overdue, but she seemed to like it and got her first bass smell on her hands. ❤️🎣

@sarah.ks.moore

What a week! What a Final Day! What a comeback! What a lake! 

Congrats to @drewbentonfishing coming from 10th to 1st to win his 2nd Elite title of his career. I’ve never seen so many anglers have a legit shot at a win within the last hour of a tournament. 

The words that were written for you and the words you spoke were an amazing representation of God’s power to make the impossible, possible. #basselite #fishing #bassmaster #lakemurray

Congratulations to @lukepalmerfishing! He takes the title at the 2023 @bass_nation Elite at Santee Cooper with 96 pounds, 14 ounces. He won by 14-3, the 6th largest margin of victory in Elite Series history! What a week for the Oklahoma pro. 

#bassmaster #santeecooper #basselite

Saltwater Ron returns. Today is Day 1 of the 2023 Louisiana Gulf Coast Billfish Classic out of Grand Isle + Venice, LA. @sportfishingchampionship @lgcbc 

4-6 PM ET on CBS Sports Network

Man what a final day! @willdavisjrfishing_ gets it done on the home pond with 62-12 by just 2 OUNCES. Congratulations on the phenomenal performance and making the home crowd proud. 

People were worried about this one on the schedule but boy was it one of the most fun events to cover of the year. @bass_nation #basselite #bassmaster #laylake

Despite the postponed event in Orange Beach, we talked with Capt’n Patrick Ivie on @breathe_easy_fishing_team about currently being top dog of the @sportfishingchampionship Gulf Division heading into the next stop of the season. 

We will hit the heart of the Gulf season when we have back-to-back-to-back events in Mississippi, Alabama and Florida in a few weeks. #SFC #SportFishingChampionship

Marlow is having a blast at the beach 😂😂

We are too @sarah.ks.moore
Where Marlow is, so too are the photo shoots.

Brock gets it done! @brockmosleyfishing leaves no doubt and wins his first @bass_nation Elite Series title with 44-3 at the Sabine River. That’s a 1st, 2nd and 12th for Mosley in Orange, Texas. Congratulations! I absolutely love covering the Sabine River events. #bassmaster #basselite #sabineriver

📍Biloxi, Mississippi

Home of the 27th @mgcbc and the 2nd stop of the Gulf Division for the @sportfishingchampionship 🤙🏻🤙🏻😮‍💨😮‍💨

The sun set on the Top 3 SFC finishers from the 27th running of the @mgcbc. Team All In, Quantified and Rebecca started the week side by side at the docks and ended the same way on the leaderboard.

1. @teamallinfishing - 4 blues (1400 pts)
2. Quantified - 8 whites, 3 sails (1225 pts)
3. @therebecca_pa - 3 blues, 1 sail (1125 pts)

@sportfishingchampionship #SFC

Nuggets win, Nuggets win, NUGGETS WIN!

For the 1st time in my life, my favorite sports team ended the season as CHAMPIONS! What a fun year, what a fun team! @nuggets

Knocked a lil feature shoot you’ll see soon with @buddygrossfishing and @tristin_williams_. 

@bass_nation ✖️ @phoenixbassboats

Leg 2️⃣ of the road-trip took us to @huntershryockfishing’s domain! Talked motocross, bass fishing, video editing and more in this @bass_nation and @phoenixbassboats collab. #basselite #fishing #bassmaster

Had a great time in Biloxi, MS last week with my saltwater peeps. Had the privilege to interview Governor Reeves about fishing, the progress Mississippi is trying to make and more. 

🎥: @sportfishingchampionship 
#SFC #Biloxi #MGCBC @mgcbc

The last leg of my road trip took me to a few guys in the Carolina’s. 

Arey ➡️ New ➡️ Cherry

Knocked out some content you’ll see on Bassmaster.com and @bass_nation 🤙🏻

And now we drive through the night to see the girls at home.
To the one who made me Da Da, thank you for helping me realize a dream. Being your dad and being a dad is something I prayed about for a long time. ❤️

The fellas minus Noah. 

📍The Vegas Crib

What a week in Vegas with @ibclrstudents and @favorcitylv. I have so much to talk about and share over the next few days, but all I can say is God is so faithful. He moves mountains and equips those who love him and passionately seek him. These kids mean the world to me and I am blessed to serve with them.

Vegas taught me…

“Love one another with brotherly affection. Outdo one another in showing honor. Do not be slothful in zeal, be fervent in spirit, serve the Lord.” - Romans 12:10-11
A lot happened in my 20’s and I CANT WAIT to see what God has for me in my 30’s. Never stop pursuing and being obedient. Keep the main thing, the main thing!

“Therefore, confess your sins to one another and pray for one another, that you may be healed. The prayer of a righteous person has great power as it is working.” 
- James 5:16
We call this: Marlow’s happy place
7/16/16 — 7 summers we’ve been married. Doesn’t make me sad one bit! Thankful that God gave me you (y’all) 🙌🏻❤️
Dinner out with Dad and Marlow’s big brothers and sisters ❤️

What a week! @joeycifuentesfishing wins the 2023 Bassmaster Elite at Lake St. Clair with 91 pounds, 8 ounces! He spent the whole week in the Top 5 and went against the grain to win his 2nd Elite event of his Rookie season! @bass_nation 

🟡 91-8 beats the 2017 mark of 88-8 for highest Elite winning weight at St. Clair. 

🟡 There were 114 20-pound bags this week. 

🟡100% limit rate of 264 possible bags

Yesterday was incredible. Directed/produced another @phoenixbassboats Pro Diary videos for the series with @tristin_williams_. 

This time we were in Minnesota with @joshdouglasfishing aka Dougie and he took care of us in a big way. He busted his butt so we could bust em after we finished the shoot and boy did we. 10+ 4’s and a 23 pound bag in about an hour before the sun dipped behind the horizon. Worked so hard we had to get a second dinner 😂🔨
Hey, can you keep growing up, but not grow up at the same time? Is that possible?

I’m gonna miss this bunch a whole lot. When I joined this group in the fall of 2018, I thought I was doing them a favor as a leader, but I never knew how important they would end up being in my life. We’ve served others both here and far together, we’ve developed a greater faith together, we had so many laughs and serious moments, I’ve watched you go from kids to adults (kinda) and I cant wait for the next steps of your journeys. 

Thank you for the memories. Thank you for letting me be apart of your life. Thank you for being my friend when I needed one. Thank you for loving my family as your own. Thank you for the countless hours, I don’t regret a single one.

Y’all are the best. My first kids ❤️
Same duo, same breakfast spot, both getting so old! Time is flyin!

Congratulations to @fujita_kyoya, officially a Bassmaster Elite Series Champion! The sacrifices from our international anglers are unparalleled in other sports. It’s incredible. His 4th Top 10 this year finally nets him a victory. The man is a magician and has finely tuned his craft for sure. @bass_nation

What a wild Thursday! Had the opportunity to do LIVE on two different JM Productions today. 

We did @bass_nation LIVE  for 7 hours at the St. Lawrence River where we saw 48 20-pound bags and a 25-year record fall as Bryant Smith caught 29-5 today to lead. 

Then we jumped over to the @sportfishingchampionship feed for 3 hours where we kicked off the 70th running of the IBT in Puerto Rico on CBS Sports and teams were catching Blue Marlin just 5 miles off the coast. 

Grateful where God has me in this season of life with the people I’m around.

Had some guests jump on the set to drop some sick lines today for the Mid Day Report😂

Hard to have a bad time when you have a room full of group leaders like @mark_zona_fishing, Ole Tom, @petermillerfishing and @robbiefloyd329

What a way to end the 2023 @bass_nation Elite Series season. Busting over 100 pounds on smallmouth again and @patrickwaltersfishing taking home yet another Blue Trophy and a Century Club belt. 

Known you for a long time, saw some of this coming, but your never-make-an-excuse attitude is motivating and a reason you’ve been so successful. Just get er done, roll tide baby. 

Big time tourney where Walters gets his 3rd 100-pound event, tying AMart-Ike-Kennedy for 2nd all time. 105 pounds ranks 30th in all-time weight as well and was higher than both of his Fork totals 🤯 Atta boy Patty Walt.

Paying attention to my family >>> Worrying about the fishing industry 

#stayfocused
My two people 😍

We are watching the moves happen this week at Watts Bar. Bobby Lane making a move.

You can name em. I'd take any combination of 9-10 anglers from the Opens this year as our 2024 Rookie class on the Elite Series. 1-10 is phenomenal, same goes for 11-20, 21-30, 31-40, 41-50.

Fields have been stacked with easily recognizable names. Excited to see these final three @bass_nation Opens play out.

Who enjoyed having @markmenendezbass in studio, co-hosting the @bass_nation Open at Watts Bar last weekend?

LIVE doesn’t stop. We will have @greghackneyfishing this coming weekend for the Lake of the Ozarks show on Sunday.
In that season of life where you cant tell us nothin’ 😍😂

Had a blast with @greghackneyfishing and @mksuchan in studio for Championship Sunday of the Bassmaster Open at Lake of the Ozarks. Who enjoyed having the Hack Attack on this side of the camera breaking it down. Congrats to @kgpfishing on the win and Classic berth, what a fun final day.
#15 on the court and #1 in our hearts. Had to document getting to see Auntie Allison and her Tech team take on OBU last night. Grateful my first kids love my first kid 💚
Life lately ❤️
Don’t wanna forget these moments.

1 YEAR
365 DAYS

Last October I was getting tired of exclusively reading children’s books to Marlow, so I wanted to figure out a plan to read something new and not the same stuff over and over. 

Well, the Bible is a perfect place to start. The Bible App Verse of the Day notifications give us a great foundation of diversity day to day. 

I’m proud of us, that no matter if I was in person or on FaceTime that we made it one complete year. Now, I never want to stop. Let’s make it 3,600 days, 5,000? Why stop?

The Lord spoke to me where I was at on so many days, he gave me words to consider and pass along to friends and something to look forward to daily. Cant wait for day 366 tomorrow.
Putting in some VO work for some @bass_nation shows you’ll see around Christmas!

It’s tournament week! 2023 @rileyscatch Cup event is this weekend. See y’all there!

🟡 Meeting - November 17th at Elevation Church in Cornelius, NC @rileyscatch

See you tonight! @rileyscatch at 6 pm at Elevation Church in Cornelius, NC.

Great night of fishing talk, giving back to the community and sharing about Riley’s dream and Jesus!

Proclaiming the name of Jesus! God is so good to us even though we are so undeserving. 

This weekend was the 9th annual Riley’s Cup and I had the honor to speak at the Friday night meeting and share the love of Jesus to 400 kids and adults. Sharing Jesus at a fishing meeting, what an unbelievable opportunity. I pray those seeds fall into good soil for the families and to cultivate and for God to take hold in their lives. 

Fishing was pretty good as well as a couple good bags hit the scales. The kids also packed 200 tackle boxes that will be given out to kids in the Charlotte region who may not have any fishing gear or have never been introduced to fishing 🙏🏻🎣
See a pile of leaves, put baby in em 🍂🍁😍
Thankful and grateful for so much. Truly blessed in many ways.
Mama made bread! Big fans over here.

Serving with your spouse is an underrated aspect to a strong marriage. I sometimes don’t serve enough in the home voluntarily, but as a team, I’d serve with Sarah any and everywhere. That’s my partner in crime! Once a month we serve in the church nursery with future believers and generations of little ones. @sarah.ks.moore

Knocked out Step 1 of something really cool that’s rolling out this year for @collegebass. Quick, but productive trip with @kylejessie and @logan.crumley highlighting the Eagles over at @cnanglers 🦅🤙🏻 #TalonsUp
We love us some lights >>>
Yea, she’s the best 😍🥺

Been together a long time. So thankful for all those days. I’ve learned so much about you, even more so, over the last year and a half. Glad we got to dress up fancy and shoot straw wrappers at each other for date night. @sarah.ks.moore

The lights! She loves the lights! We do too. 

📍LR Zoo 🐅🐘🦙🦍🦧
Merry Christmas ya filthy animals

2023. Another year where the Lord showed up and was present. But this year, I actually showed up to meet him more than I ever have. For the first time in 30 years of life, I read the Bible every day this year and I’m grateful my ladies were a part of that experience as well. 

The best gift I received this year was Marlow saying Jesus and Bible during Christmas week. 

Sarah is more than I deserve in a spouse. 

Like we talked about today at church, my past Uncertainty has turned to Certainty through Trust and Patience. Lord always shows up, just not when we want or expect. Never early, never late. Always on time. I’m banking on more of his clutchness in 2024 and beyond. 

To God be the Glory.

Follower of Christ ✝️

@Bass_Nation and @sportfishingchampionship 🎣
